title: CLAMP in Wonderland
synopsis: A short video set to music featuring many of CLAMP's most popular anime and manga characters (at the time of its production). The accompanying song tells of a Wonderland filled with imagination, magic, and dreams.
characters: ['Sumeragi, Subaru', 'Shirou, Kamui', 'Sakurazuka, Seishirou', 'Shidou, Hikaru', 'Arisugawa, Sorata', 'Ryuuzaki, Umi', 'Hououji, Fuu', 'Kishu, Arashi', 'Sumeragi, Hokuto', 'Ashura']
